We are living in the digital world where Artificial Intelligence is taking over all tasks. This has, in turn, culminated to the retrenchment of many people because manpower is no longer relevant. Value addition and minimising the cost is what every business entity wants to achieve. But are we really ready to embrace digital technology? Do we have necessary skills to accommodate the same? Are our institutions ready to empower a generation? ICT ministry should fund local institutions of higher learning to sponsor courses that will allow people to adopt digital jobs.  Writer and blogger